data.title: Watch USA on compulsory balance beam at Atlanta 96
data.meta_description: Watch the American compulsory balance beam rotation from Atlanta 1996. The 'Magnificent Seven' went on to win the U.S.'s first women's Olympic team gold.
data.text:
WATCH: The U.S. women's compulsory balance beam rotation from Atlanta 1996. Dubbed the 'Magnificent Seven', the squad went on to win the United States' first... women's Olympic team gold medal. Shannon Miller led the American team in this rotation, scoring a 9.737.
